org.apache.ignite.ml.inference.builder

Interface AsyncModelBuilder

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    IgniteDistributedModelBuilder, ThreadedModelBuilder
    Functional Interface:
    This is a functional interface and can therefore be used as the assignment target for a lambda expression or method reference.

    @FunctionalInterface
public interface AsyncModelBuilder
    Builder of asynchronous inference model. Uses specified model reader (see ModelReader) and mode parser (see ModelParser) to build a model.
